{"title":"We’re Sending Out Free Copies of ‘Love Letter, Turbo’ to Radavist Membership Subscribers","link":"https://theradavist.com/love-letter-turbo/","date":1738695128000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-8.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-8.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>For our first Radavist Membership giveaway, we’re going to be sending out copies of <a href=\"https://loveletterturbo.cc/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Love Letter, Turbo</em></a> to our subscribers. Let’s take a look inside this beautiful full-bleed 11 x 17 UK cycling journal below!<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>As pointed out by <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/petor-favourite-products-2024/\" target=\"_blank\">Petor in his Year-End Recap</a>, <em>Love Letter, Turbo</em> is a stunning alt-cycling art journal.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-4.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-4.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The photos are printed full-bleed on heavy stock paper, making flipping through its pages with a cuppa a fine way to spend some quiet time in your busy life. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>We have a few print magazine giveaways planned this year and <em>Love Letter, Turbo</em> is a fine way to kick things off. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-9.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-9.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-9.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-9.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-10.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-10.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Love-Letter-Turbo-Magazine-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The ladder stitch binding is a nice touch and thank you for the wonderful plug, team!</p>\n<p><strong>There are more than a few copies we will be sending out to Radavist Membership subscribers, so if you haven’t signed up to support our independent Reportage, <a href=\"https://radbazaar.theradavist.com/subscribe\" target=\"_blank\">do so here at the Rad Bazaar</a>. Once we get in our mailers, we’ll drop some lucky winners an email to get their mailing address. </strong></p>\n<p>If you have supported us over the past 15 months, we really appreciate it!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/love-letter-turbo/\">We’re Sending Out Free Copies of ‘Love Letter, Turbo’ to Radavist Membership Subscribers</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"d3ff1dcb0ed999246c81006360918b019a1743be46633a42c6d956f03ec8405c","category":"Cycling"}